title: New minion icon
body: I did the ritual but didn't get the icon so far, did i do something wrong or will it take time?And how can i know when i get it? Thank you in advance.

replies.body: I did the mini game and i won a game of doom bots is this what i need to do to get the icon or something is missing?

We're sending the Teemoing Icons out until **November 17th**. If you don't have it by then, you can submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll help you out.
